when hustlin tha \f(CW\*(C`Configure\*(C'\fR script. Right back up in yo muthafuckin ass. See also \*(L"\-f\*(R" up in perlrun.
.ie n .SS """Config.pm"" is now much smaller."
.el .SS "\f(CWConfig.pm\fP is now much smaller."
